# ============================================
# 🎯 Final Notes
# ============================================

# This .gitignore is designed for:
# - Python backend (FastAPI)
# - React frontend
# - PostgreSQL database
# - Docker containers
# - Various IDEs and editors

# Keep this file up to date as you add new
# technologies and dependencies to your project.

# Happy coding! 🚀
